  dialogueName: Bad Ending
  type: 3
  lines:
  - text: That's it?
  - text: I expected much more from you.
  - text: You barely made me dizzy.
  - text: A deal is a deal...
  - text: ...and you lost.
  - text: You won't get a single coin from me.
